		"description": "\n[4.14.35-1902.306.2.4]\n- IB/mlx5: Reduce max order of memory allocated for xlt update (Praveen Kumar Kannoju)  [Orabug: 32751655]\n\n[4.14.35-1902.306.2.3]\n- uek-rpm: Update SecureBoot Digicert 2021 certificates (Somasundaram Krishnasamy)  [Orabug: 32754857] \n- IB/mlx5: Use fragmented QP's buffer for in-kernel users (Guy Levi)  [Orabug: 32753250] \n- net/mlx5: Refactor fragmented buffer struct fields and init flow (Tariq Toukan)  [Orabug: 32753250]\n\n[4.14.35-1902.306.2.2]\n- A/A Bonding: Increase number and interval of GARPs sent by rdmaip (Sharath Srinivasan)  [Orabug: 32133619] \n- IB/ipoib: Arm 'send_cq' to process completions in due time (Gerd Rausch)  [Orabug: 31596799] \n- mstflint_access: Update driver code to v4.15.0-1 from Github (Itay Avraham)  [Orabug: 31682347] \n- net/rds: Check for NULL rds_ibdev in rds_ib_rx() only if rds_ib_srq_enabled (Sharath Srinivasan)  [Orabug: 32133646] \n- net/rds: Force ARP flush upon RDMA_CM_EVENT_ADDR_CHANGE (Gerd Rausch)  [Orabug: 32133638]\n\n[4.14.35-1902.306.2.1]\n- IB/mlx4: disable CQ time stamping (aru kolappan)  [Orabug: 31454486]\n\n\n",
